items.headline: Become confident through easy techniques, instantly for any situation.
objectives_summary: By the end of this course you will feel super confident about yourself and aim at doing your tasks confidently which you were not able to do earlier due to lack of confidence.
In this course you will learn NLP techniques to help you boost your confidence and morale in important situations of life. The techniques taught are simple and easy to implement in your daily life.

items.title: Become assertive: improve your confidence and communication!
items.headline: Learn the basics of what self-assertiveness is, and practice it immediately!
objectives_summary: In this course, students will learn what self-assertiveness is. They will learn how a potential lack of assertiveness and authenticity is informed by many elements in our lives, such as: guilt, poor boundaries, the need to have more self-love and better priorities. After a mindset shift, students will learn to identify the right communication skills to express assertiveness. Speaking up brings an intrinsic felling of freedom that will help decrease anxiety in our lives.
